Commission will ask the European Court to take temporary 
measures against Greece, something that will undermine 
international mediator Cyrus Vance's initiative and the 
Community's political initiative through EU Commissioner Hans 
van den Broek. The spokesman said the court will give our 
country a new forum to develop its positions further. 

