<H3> <TI>   Tories United on `Free-Market Approach' to Europe </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Tories United on `Free-Market Approach' to Europe </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM1504130494 London FINANCIAL TIMES in English 15 Apr 94 p 
9--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

