<H3> <TI>   Reynolds to Provide `Far-Reaching Guarantees' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Reynolds to Provide `Far-Reaching Guarantees' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TB1804100894 London THE TIMES in English 18 Apr 94 p 2--FOR 
