  [Text] Two strong explosions rocked Kolonaki [an Athens 
neighborhood] at 0450 today. The explosive devices were planted 
under two French Embassy cars at 9 Kherson Street and 14 Stathas 
Street. Explosives experts defused a third device under another 
car. No organization has claimed responsibility for planting 
the explosive devices. 

