  [Text] Bosnian Serb forces are once more shelling the city 
of Gorazde, killing civilians. 
  Meanwhile, Italian Defense Minister Fabio Fabbri has said: 
We have instructed our bases to move toward full alert status. 
  Fabbri added that he did not rule out the possibility of 
going to Vicenza [north-east Italy] to make direct contact with 
the NATO command. 

